            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "A heartfelt thank you to 'Crescent Castle Public School'\n\nI am proud to call myself a 'Crescentian', having been part of it  from LKG to Grade 12. Crescent has not only nurtured my academic growth but has also shaped my character. The dedication of my teachers went beyond textbooks. They instilled in us the values of discipline, respect, and integrity. Even simple routines like checking our nails have made a huge impact!\n\nI extend my deepest gratitude to all my teachers and the school management for making my school days both memorable and enriching. Thank you for the invaluable lessons and for making this journey a truly unforgettable one.",
